<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseInsect">
    <defName>MorrowRim_AlbinoSpider</defName>
    <label>albino spider</label>
    <description>A relatively large pale spider, usually found living within deep, and likely untouched, cave networks.\n\nThe albino spider is a somewhat strange creature, though not for the reason one may expect. Their body appears to be highly reactive to the environment, causing them to rapidly mutate when exposed to certain stimuli. A well versed member of Great House Telvanni may be able to use this to their advantage.\n\nThe albino spider is incredibly fragile, and their corpses will often fall apart after death. If you are lucky their abdomen may remain undamaged.</description>
